Deployment Instructions
div()
1. Install QuickMail 2007 + CME.
2. Connect domain.
3. Connect to central server
4. Charge customer.
5. Send temporary login to admin panel to customer.
div()
About CME
div()
CME (Custom Mial Extensions) is a collection of third-party plugins that customises the QuickMail server how we want. 
It includes MX masking and security extensions. The .zip file is on our FTP server (ftp.mail.com).
